name: MyStylist
0:
”Alexa, open my stylist”
”What should I wear today in Atlanta?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my stylist
des:
When you're picking out an outfit in the busy morning, knowing the weather sometimes doesn't cut it. When we were young, we had our parents stop us at the front door to change our outfits if we dressed too cold or too hot for the weather but when you're on your own, picking the right outfit can be tough. But Alexa can help you!
Simply launch My Stylist and ask Alexa "What should I wear today?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
